body:
Tutoring

This post is dedicated to all of those who feel lost with homework, school, or life in general! 

 Hello! This post as I said above is dedicated to all who seriously need some help with school, homework, studying, dealing with bullies/teachers, and life in general! I am creating this new tutoring system, where I could tutor/talk to you guys via Skype! I'm really willing to help you guys out with anything! just to give you guys a quick heads up, I quit mine craft because of school, So I know how you people may feel about playing mine craft, and still try to complete homework assignments, and get good grades, and really just stay on top of things! 

  Here is a list of all the the things I'm willing to help you all with:
  • Anything related to history (History, Geography, Humanities) Don't get mad if I get carried away sometimes xP
  • English: I take honors english, and I can help you guys with annotations, writing essays, and critical reading!
  • Math: Well, i'm sorry! I am not the best at algebra! I can help with geometry though!
  • Spanish: I take spanish 2 currently, and I really can help anyone who desperately needs some help!
  • Science: I can totally help with bio, a little in chemistry.. that's pretty much it!
  • P.E: Yes. I actually can help you guys with this. Overall, I can help you guys with proper stretching, eating, and good exercise! Im also an experienced athlete, so any questions about sports, I'm here to help!
  • I'm really good with handling bullies! (not physically) Ask me for help!
  • Life help. this includes: Organization, good studying habits, advice about anything related to school/sports/handling harsh people in your life!
  That is pretty much the big list of opportunities I'm willing to help you guys with!

 Here is a quick thing about my contact info:

  •  I use Skype, and I'm usually online in the weekends, or nights that I have no homework/swim meets
  • If, I'm not online, but you guys need my help, send me a message, or a photo of the problem you need help with
  • My real name is Christian! Just wanted to let you guys know, because my Skype has my name in it, and I was just letting you guys know beforehand, so that you don't get all creeped out before contacting me!
  • Here is my Skype: christian.hartley14
  • If this does not work, contact my alternative account at: shamrocky_
  I'm really new to this, but I am truly happy to answer all questions you guys have! I hope that you guys will use this, to not only benefit yourselves right now, but your future as well! 

Lots of <3 


-SenorSombrero
